Scrape from URL and get match_data dataframe.

URL <- "https://www.sportinglife.com/football/live/60036/"
League <- c('Sky Bet League One') #Manually Set league
team_of_interest <- "Charlton Athletic"
other_colour <- "cyan2"
home_fill <- '#ff0000'
away_fill <- '#1a4990'

sportinglife <- read_html(paste(URL, "commentary",sep="")) #set URL
sportinglife_stats <- read_html(paste(URL, "stats",sep=""))

team_names <-  sportinglife %>% #Get match summary as html node
  html_nodes('.footballMatchSummaryDef') %>%
  html_text() %>% 
  gsub("^\\s+|\\s+$", "", .)
both_teams = team_names #Set team names as both_teams string

home_team = unlist(strsplit(both_teams, split=' v ', fixed=TRUE))[1] #Extract home team before 'v'
away_team = unlist(strsplit(both_teams, split=' v ', fixed=TRUE))[2] #Extract data after 'v'
away_team = unlist(strsplit(away_team, split=League[1], fixed=TRUE))[1] #Strip league from away team
#team_names <- data.frame(team_names) #Put match summary in a dataframe

match_events <-  sportinglife %>% #Get events as html node
    html_nodes('.detail-col') %>%
    html_text() %>% 
    gsub("^\\s+|\\s+$", "", .)
events <- data.frame(match_events) #Set events values as items scraped above


match_time <-  sportinglife %>% #Get times as html node
  html_nodes('.match-time') %>%
  html_text() %>% 
  gsub("^\\s+|\\s+$", "", .)
match_data <- data.frame(match_time) #Set time values as items scraped above

Tidy up match_data to get match data that matches website

del_last <- nrow(events) #Get total number of rows

events <- data.frame(events[-del_last,]) #delete last row from  events dataframe
events <- data.frame(events[-1,]) #delete first row from events dataframe

match_data$event <- events #Combine columns to get dataframe as seen on website

colnames(match_data)[1] <- 'Time' #Set column name
colnames(match_data[,2]) <- 'Event'

ifelse(team_of_interest == "Charlton",team_of_interest_c <- "red3",team_of_interest_c <- other_colour )
## [1] "cyan2"
ifelse(home_team == team_of_interest, other_team <- away_team, other_team <- home_team)
## [1] "Southend United"
ifelse(grepl(team_of_interest,home_team),home_colour <- team_of_interest_c,home_colour <- "cyan2")
## [1] "cyan2"
ifelse(grepl(team_of_interest,away_team),away_colour <- team_of_interest_c,away_colour <- "cyan2")
## [1] "cyan2"
rm(events,sportinglife,del_last,League,match_events,match_time,team_names,URL,both_teams)
for (i in 1:length(match_data$event)){
  ifelse(grepl(paste(team_of_interest, ")", sep=""), match_data$event[i])==TRUE,
         match_data$team[i] <- team_of_interest,
         match_data$team[i] <- other_team)
}


stopwords <- unlist(read.delim('players.txt'))

#Removing stopwords from event for preparation of getting player names
x  = match_data$event
x  =  removeWords(as.character(x),stopwords)
match_data$player <- x

match_data$player <- word(match_data$player,1,sep = "\\(")

for (i in 1:length(match_data$player)){
  ifelse(grepl("\\.",match_data$player[i])==TRUE,
         (match_data$player[i] <- unlist(lapply(strsplit(match_data$player[i], '.', fixed = TRUE), '[', 2))),
         match_data$player[i])
}

match_data$player <- as.factor(gsub(" ", "", match_data$player, fixed = TRUE)) #Removing white space for better factorisation
match_data$player <- as.factor(gsub("!", "", match_data$player, fixed = TRUE)) #Removing exclamation marks for better factorisation

for (i in 1:length(match_data$event)){
  ifelse(grepl("Attempt",match_data$event[i]) | grepl("Goal",match_data$event[i]) | grepl("shot",match_data$event[i])==TRUE,
         match_data$type[i] <- "shot",
         ifelse(grepl("Foul",match_data$event[i])==TRUE,
         match_data$type[i] <- "Foul",
         ifelse(grepl("hand ball",match_data$event[i],ignore.case = TRUE)==TRUE,
         match_data$type[i] <- "hand ball",
         ifelse(grepl("substitution",match_data$event[i],ignore.case = TRUE)==TRUE,
         match_data$type[i] <- "substitution",
         ifelse(grepl("red card",match_data$event[i],ignore.case = TRUE)==TRUE,
         match_data$type[i] <- "card",
         ifelse(grepl("wins a free kick",match_data$event[i],ignore.case = TRUE)==TRUE,
         match_data$type[i] <- "free kick won",
         ifelse(grepl("First half begins",match_data$event[i],ignore.case = TRUE)==TRUE,
         match_data$type[i] <- "start of first half",
         ifelse(grepl("First half ends",match_data$event[i],ignore.case = TRUE)==TRUE,
         match_data$type[i] <- "end of first half",
         ifelse(grepl("Second half begins",match_data$event[i],ignore.case = TRUE)==TRUE,
         match_data$type[i] <- "start of second half",
         ifelse(grepl("second half ends",match_data$event[i],ignore.case = TRUE)==TRUE,
         match_data$type[i] <- "end of first half",
         ifelse(grepl("corner",match_data$event[i],ignore.case = TRUE)==TRUE,
         match_data$type[i] <- "corner",
         ifelse(grepl("yellow card",match_data$event[i])==TRUE,
         match_data$type[i] <- "card",
         match_data$type[i] <- "error"))))))))))))
}
for (i in 1:length(match_data$event)){
ifelse(grepl("Own goal",match_data$event[i],ignore.case = TRUE)==TRUE,
         match_data$type[i] <- "Own goal",
         match_data$type[i] <- match_data$type[i])
}


for (i in 1:length(match_data$event)){
  ifelse(grepl("left footed",match_data$event[i])==TRUE,
         match_data$kind[i] <- "left footed",
         ifelse(grepl("right footed",match_data$event[i])==TRUE,
         match_data$kind[i] <- "right footed",
         ifelse(grepl("red card",match_data$event[i],ignore.case = TRUE)==TRUE,
         match_data$kind[i] <- "red card",
         ifelse(grepl("yellow card",match_data$event[i],ignore.case = TRUE)==TRUE,
         match_data$kind[i] <- "yellow card",
         ifelse(grepl("header",match_data$event[i])==TRUE,
         match_data$kind[i] <- "header",
         match_data$kind[i] <- "error")))))
}

for (i in 1:length(match_data$event)){
  ifelse(grepl("outside the box",match_data$event[i])==TRUE,
         match_data$loc[i] <- "outside the box",
         ifelse(grepl("left side of the box",match_data$event[i])==TRUE,
         match_data$loc[i] <- "left side of the box",
         ifelse(grepl("penalty",match_data$event[i],ignore.case = TRUE)==TRUE,
         match_data$loc[i] <- "penalty",
         ifelse(grepl("centre of the box",match_data$event[i])==TRUE,
         match_data$loc[i] <- "centre of the box",
         ifelse(grepl("difficult angle and long range",match_data$event[i])==TRUE,
         match_data$loc[i] <- "speculative",
         ifelse(grepl("right footed shot from more than 40 yards",match_data$event[i])==TRUE,
         match_data$loc[i] <- "speculative",
         ifelse(grepl("long range on the left",match_data$event[i])==TRUE,
         match_data$loc[i] <- "speculative",
         ifelse(grepl("difficult angle on the right",match_data$event[i])==TRUE,
         match_data$loc[i] <- "tight angle - right",
         ifelse(grepl("difficult angle on the left",match_data$event[i])==TRUE,
         match_data$loc[i] <- "tight angle - left",
         ifelse(grepl("more than 35 yards",match_data$event[i])==TRUE,
         match_data$loc[i] <- "speculative",
         ifelse(grepl("right side of the box",match_data$event[i])==TRUE,
         match_data$loc[i] <- "right side of the box",
         ifelse(grepl(" right side of the six yard box",match_data$event[i])==TRUE,
         match_data$loc[i] <- " right side of the six yard box",
         ifelse(grepl("left side of the six yard box",match_data$event[i])==TRUE,
         match_data$loc[i] <- "left side of the six yard box",
         ifelse(grepl("centre of the six yard box",match_data$event[i])==TRUE,
         match_data$loc[i] <- "centre of the six yard box",
         ifelse(grepl("close range",match_data$event[i])==TRUE,
         match_data$loc[i] <- "close range",
         match_data$loc[i] <- "error")))))))))))))))
}
shots <- filter(match_data, type=='shot')
shots <- shots %>% arrange(-row_number())
for (i in 1:length(shots$kind)){
  ifelse(grepl("left footed",shots$kind[i])==TRUE,
         shots$coeff[i] <- 0.98,
         ifelse(grepl("right footed",shots$kind[i])==TRUE,
         shots$coeff[i] <- 0.98,
         ifelse(grepl("header",shots$kind[i])==TRUE,
         shots$coeff[i] <- 0.89,
         shots$coeff[i] <- "error")))
}

for (i in 1:length(shots$loc)){
  ifelse(grepl("outside the box",shots$loc[i])==TRUE,
         shots$adj_dis[i] <- 29.7,
         ifelse(grepl("left side of the box",shots$loc[i])==TRUE,
         shots$adj_dis[i] <- 18.4,
         ifelse(grepl("penalty",shots$loc[i])==TRUE,
         shots$adj_dis[i] <- NA,
         ifelse(grepl("centre of the box",shots$loc[i])==TRUE,
         shots$adj_dis[i] <- 10.3,
         ifelse(grepl("speculative",shots$loc[i])==TRUE,
         shots$adj_dis[i] <- 35,
         ifelse(grepl("tight angle - right",shots$loc[i])==TRUE,
         shots$adj_dis[i] <- 35,
         ifelse(grepl("tight angle - left",shots$loc[i])==TRUE,
         shots$adj_dis[i] <- 35,
         ifelse(grepl("speculative",shots$loc[i])==TRUE,
         shots$adj_dis[i] <- 35,
         ifelse(grepl("right side of the box",shots$loc[i])==TRUE,
         shots$adj_dis[i] <- 18.4,
         ifelse(grepl(" right side of the six yard box",shots$loc[i])==TRUE,
         shots$adj_dis[i] <- 3.6,
         ifelse(grepl("left side of the six yard box",shots$loc[i])==TRUE,
         shots$adj_dis[i] <- 3.6,
         ifelse(grepl("centre of the six yard box",shots$loc[i])==TRUE,
         shots$adj_dis[i] <- 3.2,
         ifelse(grepl("close range",shots$loc[i])==TRUE,
         shots$adj_dis[i] <- 3,
         shots$adj_dis[i] <- "error")))))))))))))
}

shots$adj_dis <- as.numeric(shots$adj_dis)



for (i in 1:length(shots$kind)){
  ifelse(grepl("left footed",shots$kind[i])==TRUE,
         shots$formula_coeff[i] <- -0.12,
         ifelse(grepl("right footed",shots$kind[i])==TRUE,
         shots$formula_coeff[i] <- -0.12,
         ifelse(grepl("header",shots$kind[i])==TRUE,
         shots$formula_coeff[i] <- -0.24,
         shots$formula_coeff[i] <- "error")))
}

for (i in 1:length(shots$loc)){
  ifelse(shots$loc[i] == "penalty", shots$xG[i] <- 0.76,
         shots$xG[i] <- shots$coeff[i] * exp(shots$formula_coeff[i] * shots$adj_dis[i]))
}

home_xg <- filter(shots, team == home_team)
away_xg <- filter(shots, team == away_team)

home_xg$cum_xg <- cumsum(home_xg$xG)
away_xg$cum_xg <- cumsum(away_xg$xG)

home_xg %>% group_by(player) %>% summarise(total_xG = sum(xG)) %>% arrange(desc(total_xG)) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x= reorder(player, -total_xG), y=total_xG)) +
  geom_bar(stat="identity", fill=home_fill) +
  labs(x=paste('Player - ', home_team, sep=""),
       y='Total xG',
       title=paste("xG by player \nTotal xG = ", round(home_xg$cum_xg[nrow(home_xg)],2),sep=""),
       subtitle=paste(home_team," vs ",away_team,sep=""),
       caption= "@AddicksAnalytic") +
  guides(fill='none') +
  theme_minimal() +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1, vjust = 0.5)) +
  theme(plot.caption=element_text(size=8, face="italic", color="grey47"))

away_xg %>% group_by(player) %>% summarise(total_xG = sum(xG)) %>% arrange(desc(total_xG)) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x= reorder(player, -total_xG), y=total_xG)) +
  geom_bar(stat="identity", fill=away_fill) +
  labs(x=paste('Player - ', away_team, sep=""),
       y='Total xG',
       title=paste("xG by player \nTotal xG = ", round(away_xg$cum_xg[nrow(away_xg)],2),sep=""),
       subtitle=paste(home_team," vs ",away_team,sep=""),
       caption= "@AddicksAnalytic") +
  guides(fill='none') +
  theme_minimal() +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1, vjust = 0.5)) +
  theme(plot.caption=element_text(size=8, face="italic", color="grey47"))

shots %>% group_by(player,team) %>% summarise(total_xG = sum(xG)) %>% arrange(desc(total_xG)) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x= reorder(player, -total_xG), y=total_xG, fill=team)) +
  scale_fill_manual(values = c("Charlton Athletic" = "#FF0000", "Southend United" = "#1a4990")) +
  geom_bar(stat="identity") +
  labs(x=paste('Player'),
       y='Total xG',
       title=paste("xG by player"),
       subtitle=paste(home_team," vs ",away_team,sep=""),
       caption= "@AddicksAnalytic") +
  guides(fill='none') +
  theme_minimal() +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1, vjust = 0.5)) +
  theme(plot.caption=element_text(size=8, face="italic", color="grey47"))

home_xg$Time <- substr(home_xg$Time, start = 1, stop = 2)
home_xg$Time <- gsub("'", '', home_xg$Time)
home_xg$Time <- as.numeric(home_xg$Time)


away_xg$Time <- substr(away_xg$Time, start = 1, stop = 2)
away_xg$Time <- gsub("'", '', away_xg$Time)
away_xg$Time <- as.numeric(away_xg$Time)

str(home_xg)
